曲《When I Gave Up On You》中。这张专辑是在纽约著名的 The Magic Shop 录音室录制的，<a href="/artists/David-Bowie">大卫·鲍伊</a>就是在这里录制了他的最后一张专辑《Blackstar》。</p><p>今年，“Heart Of Glass”热门制作人进行了一些现场表演，其中包括今年夏天早些时候在哈利法克斯 Piece Hall 举行的两场演出。他们还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-jones-bryan-adams-sting-and-blondie-for-very-first-plymouth-summer-sessions-buy-tickets-3550015">第一届普利茅斯夏季音乐节上</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-jones">Tom Jones</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/bryan-adams">Bryan Adams</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madness">Madness</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">Sting</a>一起演出，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">Duran Duran</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/interpol">Interpol</a>一起在加利福尼亚州帕萨迪纳举办的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-interpol-blondie-headline-cruel-world-festival-2024-3553447">Cruel World Festival</a>上亮相。</p><p>去年，该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blondie-glastonbury-2023-setlist-photos-quotes-videos-3461148">在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上表演了一场热门演出</a>，期间他们向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/donna-summer">唐娜·萨默</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sex-pistols">性手枪乐队</a>致敬。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DA1V2n0PiPY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div st